00:18:46.040 --> 00:18:48.790
Bubble Tea

00:19:02.680 --> 00:19:03.810
Let's use the photo booth, come on!

00:19:02.680 --> 00:19:05.310
ID Photos

00:19:03.810 --> 00:19:05.830
That is the wrong type of photo booth!

00:19:09.880 --> 00:19:10.810
Like this?

00:19:10.810 --> 00:19:12.560
I think so.

00:19:12.560 --> 00:19:14.220
H-Here it goes.

00:19:14.220 --> 00:19:15.060
Ready!

00:19:17.610 --> 00:19:18.820
Yeah!

00:19:19.340 --> 00:19:20.700
♥ Halloween Date ♥

00:19:19.340 --> 00:19:20.700
Mac ♥

00:19:19.340 --> 00:19:20.700
Teio!

00:19:20.700 --> 00:19:21.950
Two taiyaki please!

00:19:20.700 --> 00:19:24.820
Taiyaki

00:19:20.700 --> 00:19:24.820
300 Yen Each
 Sweet Red Bean
  Custard
  Chocolate
   Carrot

00:19:21.950 --> 00:19:24.830
Casca... err, custard filling!

00:19:28.800 --> 00:19:31.360
McQueen, you've got some on your face!

00:19:34.110 --> 00:19:35.710
I can wipe it for you.

00:19:35.710 --> 00:19:37.910
I can do it myself.

00:19:39.970 --> 00:19:42.150
Let's check that out next! Come on!

00:19:42.150 --> 00:19:42.920
All right.

00:19:45.360 --> 00:19:48.100
Today was a great deal of fun.

00:19:48.370 --> 00:19:51.600
Well, we haven't gotten 
to goof off at all lately.

00:19:51.600 --> 00:19:54.750
Yes. It was quite the 
refreshing change of pace.

00:19:54.750 --> 00:19:57.360
This should allow me to 
focus on training again.

00:19:57.360 --> 00:20:00.360
The fall races are gonna 
be coming up soon, too.

00:20:00.360 --> 00:20:04.670
The Fall Tennoushou, the Japan Cup, 
and at the end of the year...

00:20:04.670 --> 00:20:06.210
The Arima Kinen Grand Prix.

00:20:06.210 --> 00:20:09.280
The Arima Kinen is going to be so great!

00:20:09.280 --> 00:20:11.090
You're gonna be running, right?

00:20:11.090 --> 00:20:14.370
If the fans select me, of course.

00:20:14.370 --> 00:20:16.120
What about you, Teio?

00:20:16.120 --> 00:20:17.500
Me?

00:20:17.500 --> 00:20:20.860
I'm sure you'll be chosen 
in the fan survey.

00:20:20.860 --> 00:20:23.710
They'll be longing to see you run at Arima.

00:20:23.710 --> 00:20:26.990
Aw, come on, you've seen the 
times I've been managing lately.

00:20:26.990 --> 00:20:29.120
Even if I enter, there's no way I win.

00:20:30.510 --> 00:20:34.490
Not without a miracle, anyway.
 So not this time.

00:20:35.230 --> 00:20:40.020
I thought that would be the case.
 But it's still a shame.

00:20:40.020 --> 00:20:41.780
I think so, too.

00:20:42.040 --> 00:20:44.250
But someday, definitely...

00:20:46.840 --> 00:20:48.620
Yes, some day.

00:20:49.740 --> 00:20:54.070
I had a wonderful time. 
Thank you for inviting me, Teio.

00:20:54.070 --> 00:20:54.780
Yeah.

00:20:56.010 --> 00:21:00.040
I actually wanted to tell 
you something, McQueen.

00:21:00.040 --> 00:21:01.660
You did?

00:21:03.980 --> 00:21:05.680
I've been wondering all this time...

00:21:05.950 --> 00:21:09.270
what makes you different from everyone else.

00:21:10.580 --> 00:21:15.440
You see, McQueen... 
I've always looked up to you.

00:21:16.100 --> 00:21:17.580
To me?

00:21:17.580 --> 00:21:18.560
Yeah.

00:21:18.790 --> 00:21:22.160
You're so strong, so cool, 
and always so dignified.

00:21:22.160 --> 00:21:25.700
And I think I was embarrassed 
to tell you how I really feel.

00:21:25.700 --> 00:21:28.200
And kind of frustrated, too.

00:21:30.220 --> 00:21:33.910
You're really special to me, McQueen.

00:21:34.350 --> 00:21:36.410
That's how I feel now, and it's not changing.

00:21:36.940 --> 00:21:38.080
So...

00:21:38.630 --> 00:21:40.710
Thank you, McQueen!

00:21:42.260 --> 00:21:43.410
Teio...

00:21:44.940 --> 00:21:46.250
I finally said it!

00:21:46.250 --> 00:21:49.190
You look up to me?

00:21:49.190 --> 00:21:49.980
Yeah!

00:21:51.340 --> 00:21:53.100
And you've only just realized this?

00:21:55.100 --> 00:21:59.480
Because I've always looked up to you.

00:22:00.750 --> 00:22:02.380
McQueen...

00:22:09.260 --> 00:22:10.570
That is so weird!

00:22:10.570 --> 00:22:12.050
You're one to talk!

00:22:13.790 --> 00:22:14.950
Aw!

00:22:19.000 --> 00:22:22.850
Man, now that I got that off 
my chest, I'm hungry again.

00:22:22.850 --> 00:22:24.630
You want to eat again?

00:22:24.630 --> 00:22:25.880
Aw, it's fine for today!

00:22:25.880 --> 00:22:27.310
Come on, McQueen.

00:22:27.310 --> 00:22:28.130
All right.

00:22:28.130 --> 00:22:30.840
I think I'll get some grilled carrots.
How about you?

00:22:30.840 --> 00:22:34.330
I believe I'll have some shortcake, 
some baumkuchen, and some sweets!

00:22:34.330 --> 00:22:36.580
But those first two are sweets, too!

